# MANDATORY code quality verification

If you changed Python code, ALWAYS:
[ ] Run typechecker: `uv run mypy .`
[ ] Run linter/formatter: `uv run ruff check --fix .` and `uv run ruff format .`
[ ] As mentioned by other rules, still also run tests: `uv run pytest`
